  "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-main relative\"\u003e\n \u003ch1 class\u003d\"block text-[4rem] text-[var(--dark)] leading-[4.4rem] font-semibold mb-[5px]\"\u003eH\u0026agrave;n Quốc nổ s\u0026uacute;ng cảnh c\u0026aacute;o 20 binh sĩ Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n vượt bi\u0026ecirc;n\u003c/h1\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-meta flex items-center flex-wrap flex-row text-[1.3rem] leading-[2rem] font-normal text-[#999] truncate h-[30px] mb-[10px] [\u0026amp;\u0026gt;:not(:first-child)]:ml-[25px]\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"flex items-center\"\u003e\n   \u003ca href\u003d\"/bao-phap-luat-tp-hcm-plo-p114.epi\" class\u003d\"bm-card-source flex items-center shrink-0\" title\u003d\"B\u0026aacute;o Ph\u0026aacute;p Luật TP.HCM\"\u003e\n    \u003cfigure class\u003d\"image opacity-80 w-auto h-[16px]\" style\u003d\"width:55px;height:20px\" aria-label\u003d\"Logo nh\u0026agrave; xuất bản\"\u003e\n     \u003cpicture\u003e\n      \u003csource srcset\u003d\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/f12dd0420d01e45fbd10.png\" type\u003d\"image/avif\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n      \u003csource srcset\u003d\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/f12dd0420d01e45fbd10.png\" type\u003d\"image/webp\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n      \u003cimg src\u003d\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/f12dd0420d01e45fbd10.png\" alt\u003d\"B\u0026aacute;o Ph\u0026aacute;p Luật TP.HCM\" width\u003d\"176\" height\u003d\"64\" /\u003e\n     \u003c/picture\u003e\n    \u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n   \u003cspan\u003e\u003cbutton class\u003d\"relative text-[14px] leading-[normal] font-normal text-center cursor-pointer normal-case border-0 transition-button disabled:shadow-none disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed follow-button flex items-center item-star ml-[10px]\" tabindex\u003d\"0\" type\u003d\"button\" title\u003d\"Theo d\u0026otilde;i \u0026quot;PLO\u0026quot;\" aria-label\u003d\"Button\"\u003e\u003ci class\u003d\"icon inline-block font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-star text-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003ctime datetime\u003d\"2025-10-23T23:55:32.000Z\"\u003e24/10/2025\u003c/time\u003e\n  \u003ca href\u003d\"/jcs-t41375774.epi\" class\u003d\"related inline !text-[#adb5bd] hover:!text-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e20\n   \u003c!-- --\u003e li\u0026ecirc;n quan\u003c/a\u003e\n  \u003ca href\u003d\"/han-quoc-no-sung-canh-cao-20-binh-si-trieu-tien-vuot-bien-r53569630.epi\" class\u003d\"origin item-origin\" target\u003d\"_blank\" rel\u003d\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003ci class\u003d\"icon inline-block font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-copy text-[13px] mr-[5px]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGốc\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n \u003c/div\u003e\n \u003ch3 class\u003d\"sapo block text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] font-semibold text-[var(--dark)] p-[10px] bg-[#f2f4f5]\"\u003eHội đồng Tham mưu trưởng Li\u0026ecirc;n qu\u0026acirc;n H\u0026agrave;n Quốc (JCS) n\u0026oacute;i rằng qu\u0026acirc;n đội nước n\u0026agrave;y đ\u0026atilde; nổ s\u0026uacute;ng cảnh c\u0026aacute;o sau khi ph\u0026aacute;t hiện khoảng 20 binh sĩ Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n vượt bi\u0026ecirc;n.\u003c/h3\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-body text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] text-black mt-[15px] break-words overflow-hidden [\u0026amp;_h1]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h2]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h3]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h4]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h5]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_p]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;\u0026gt;div]:mb-[15px]\"\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTối 23-10, Hội đồng Tham mưu trưởng Li\u0026ecirc;n qu\u0026acirc;n \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/han-quoc-tag2475.epi\"\u003eH\u0026agrave;n Quốc\u003c/a\u003e (JCS) c\u0026aacute;o buộc khoảng 20 binh sĩ Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n đ\u0026atilde; vượt qua ranh giới qu\u0026acirc;n sự li\u0026ecirc;n Triều trong thời gian ngắn v\u0026agrave;o cuối tuần qua v\u0026agrave; quay trở về ngay sau khi binh sĩ H\u0026agrave;n Quốc bắn ph\u0026aacute;t s\u0026uacute;ng cảnh c\u0026aacute;o, theo h\u0026atilde;ng th\u0026ocirc;ng tấn \u003cem\u003eYonhap\u003c/em\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTheo JCS, c\u0026aacute;c binh sĩ \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/trieu-tien-tag552.epi\"\u003eTriều Ti\u0026ecirc;n\u003c/a\u003e đ\u0026atilde; vượt qua Đường ph\u0026acirc;n định qu\u0026acirc;n sự (MDL) tại TP bi\u0026ecirc;n giới Paju v\u0026agrave;o ng\u0026agrave;y 19-10.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url(\u0027https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png\u0027)] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\"\u003e\n   \u003ci class\u003d\"icon font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\n   \u003cbutton class\u003d\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style\u003d\"width:625px;height:416px\"\u003e\n    \u003cpicture\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/avif\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/webp\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\" Th\u0026agrave;nh phố bi\u0026ecirc;n giới Paju của H\u0026agrave;n Quốc nh\u0026igrave;n từ tr\u0026ecirc;n cao. Ảnh: YONHAP \" width\u003d\"625\" height\u003d\"416\" /\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"\u003e\u003cem\u003e Th\u0026agrave;nh phố bi\u0026ecirc;n giới Paju của H\u0026agrave;n Quốc nh\u0026igrave;n từ tr\u0026ecirc;n cao. Ảnh: YONHAP \u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eQu\u0026acirc;n đội H\u0026agrave;n Quốc theo d\u0026otilde;i hoạt động của c\u0026aacute;c binh sĩ n\u0026agrave;y đ\u0026atilde; ph\u0026aacute;t đi nhiều cảnh b\u0026aacute;o v\u0026agrave; nổ s\u0026uacute;ng cảnh c\u0026aacute;o khi c\u0026aacute;c binh sĩ tiếp tục di chuyển về ph\u0026iacute;a nam. C\u0026aacute;c qu\u0026acirc;n nh\u0026acirc;n Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n sau đ\u0026oacute; đ\u0026atilde; quay trở về ph\u0026iacute;a Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n m\u0026agrave; kh\u0026ocirc;ng c\u0026oacute; bất kỳ phản ứng cụ thể n\u0026agrave;o.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eJCS cho biết những binh sĩ n\u0026agrave;y được cho l\u0026agrave; đang l\u0026agrave;m việc gần khu vực bi\u0026ecirc;n giới, chẳng hạn như ph\u0026aacute;t quang đất hoặc g\u0026agrave;i m\u0026igrave;n trong v\u0026ugrave;ng đệm, v\u0026agrave; nhiều khả năng đ\u0026atilde; v\u0026ocirc; t\u0026igrave;nh vượt qua bi\u0026ecirc;n giới trong khi l\u0026agrave;m nhiệm vụ. Một số binh sĩ được trang bị vũ kh\u0026iacute;.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eVụ việc xảy ra c\u0026ugrave;ng ng\u0026agrave;y qu\u0026acirc;n đội H\u0026agrave;n Quốc th\u0026ocirc;ng b\u0026aacute;o bắt một binh sĩ Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n sau khi người n\u0026agrave;y vượt qua khu phi \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/the-gioi.epi\"\u003equ\u0026acirc;n sự\u003c/a\u003e giữa hai miền Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n. Đ\u0026acirc;y l\u0026agrave; vụ vượt bi\u0026ecirc;n đầu ti\u0026ecirc;n của qu\u0026acirc;n nh\u0026acirc;n Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n kể từ khi Tổng thống H\u0026agrave;n Quốc Lee Jae-myung nhậm chức hồi th\u0026aacute;ng 6.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTuy nhi\u0026ecirc;n, c\u0026aacute;c quan chức qu\u0026acirc;n đội cho biết hai vụ việc n\u0026agrave;y dường như kh\u0026ocirc;ng li\u0026ecirc;n quan đến nhau do thời gian v\u0026agrave; địa điểm kh\u0026aacute;c nhau.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003e“Qu\u0026acirc;n đội ch\u0026uacute;ng t\u0026ocirc;i đang theo d\u0026otilde;i chặt chẽ c\u0026aacute;c hoạt động của qu\u0026acirc;n đội Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n v\u0026agrave; thực hiện c\u0026aacute;c biện ph\u0026aacute;p cần thiết theo quy tr\u0026igrave;nh t\u0026aacute;c chiến\u0026quot; - một quan chức qu\u0026acirc;n đội H\u0026agrave;n Quốc n\u0026oacute;i với \u003cem\u003eYonhap\u003c/em\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTriều Ti\u0026ecirc;n chưa b\u0026igrave;nh luận về c\u0026aacute;c th\u0026ocirc;ng tin tr\u0026ecirc;n.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text body-author text-right\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTHẾ VINH\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n \u003c/div\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp\" tabindex\u003d\"-1\" role\u003d\"dialog\" aria-hidden\u003d\"true\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__bg\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__scroll-wrap\"\u003e\n   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__container\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n   \u003c/div\u003e\n   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__ui pswp__ui--hidden\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__top-bar\"\u003e\n     \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__counter\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button